</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td colspan=3>
<BR>
In related work, we have developed techniques to differentiate between
<a href="cgorphoto.html">photographic and photorealistic</a> images,
and to detect the presence of <a href="steganography.html">hidden
messages</a> embedded within digital images.

<BR><BR>

<i>(Collaborative work with 
<a href="http://www.mit.edu/~kimo"> Kimo Johnson</a>, 
<a href="http://www.cs.dartmouth.edu/~erickee"> Eric Kee</a>, 
Alin Popescu, 
<a href="http://www.cs.dartmouth.edu/~whwang">Weihong Wang</a>, and
Jeff Woodward)</i>

<BR><BR>

<b>Contact me at <a href=http://hanyfarid.org/maat/>Ma'at Consulting</a> for more
information about our consulting services.</b> <BR><BR>
</td>
